{"tid":2131374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共和黨德州眾議員拒絕戴罩後確診武漢病毒","createTime":"2020-07-29T22:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T23:34:10.000Z","uid":49776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68ac130784d81c571158eb91c75e3865c4e918d3","tid":2131374,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T22:44:42.000Z","msg":"消息人士透露，共和黨籍德州聯邦眾議員高梅特(Louie Gohmert)原訂29日上午陪同川普總統搭乘空軍一號(Air Force One)赴德州展開選舉募款，但臨行之前接受新冠病毒檢測結果呈現陽性，使得高梅特從隨行名單裡遭到緊急踢除。<br />\n今年6月間，高梅特接受美國有線電視新聞網(CNN)訪問時，曾為自己進出國會山莊經常不戴口罩辯護。他說：「我並沒有新冠病毒，直到昨天為止，我從來不曾被感染過。但是，我若是被傳染了，你永遠不會看到我沒戴口罩的。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/202007300017324181_32537.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F202007300017324181_32537.jpg&h=3af3d1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/7071039/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F7071039%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=e5497a1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/7071039/</a><br />\n<br />\n'I Have The Wuhan Virus,' Texas GOP Rep. Louie Gohmert Tests Positive For Coronavirus<br />\n<br />\nTexas Republican Rep. Louie Gohmert has tested positive for the coronavirus and is blaming wearing a mask for his diagnosis<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/videos/politics/2020/07/29/texas-louie-gohmert-positive-covid-19-raju-nr-vpx.cnn/video/playlists/this-week-in-politics/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fpolitics%2F2020%2F07%2F29%2Ftexas-louie-gohmert-positive-covid-19-raju-nr-vpx.cnn%2Fvideo%2Fplaylists%2Fthis-week-in-politics%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=9424775f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fpolitics%2F2020%2F07%2F29%2Ftexas-louie-gohmert-positive-covid-19-raju-nr-vpx.cnn%2Fvideo%2Fplaylists%2Fthis-week-in-politics%2F&h=60997b32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/videos/politics/2020/07/29/texas-louie-gohmert-positive-covid-19-raju-nr-vpx.cnn/video/playlists/this-week-in-politics/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2020/07/29/politics/louie-gohmert-tests-positive-coronavirus/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2020%2F07%2F29%2Fpolitics%2Flouie-gohmert-tests-positive-coronavirus%2Findex.html&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=d5990f5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2020%2F07%2F29%2Fpolitics%2Flouie-gohmert-tests-positive-coronavirus%2Findex.html&h=9b8d9b22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2020/07/29/politics/louie-gohmert-tests-positive-coronavirus/index.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://dfw.cbslocal.com/video/4646600-i-have-the-wuhan-virus-texas-gop-rep-louie-gohmert-tests-positive-for-coronavirus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdfw.cbslocal.com%2Fvideo%2F4646600-i-have-the-wuhan-virus-texas-gop-rep-louie-gohmert-tests-positive-for-coronavirus%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=a9fe4b73\" target=\"_blank\">https://dfw.cbslocal.com/video/4646600-i-have-the-wuhan-virus-texas-gop-rep-louie-gohmert-tests-positive-for-coronavirus/</a>"},{"pid":"4253bddaa0ace2d546d022af38a711ea80208608","tid":2131374,"uid":56610,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T22:52:35.000Z","msg":"物競天擇"},{"pid":"cf95739be8322582c88fca14fd1b04272b709dc7","tid":2131374,"uid":78016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4253bddaa0ace2d546d022af38a711ea80208608","tid":2131374,"uid":56610,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T22:52:35.000Z","msg":"物競天擇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T22:57:45.000Z","msg":"死亡率&lt;1%<br />\n好難適者生存唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde9d544f91e4b4644814bdd1074